VIGENERE CIPHER/ ENCRYPTION TOOL v1.0
*************************************

By using this application you'll be able to either encrypt or decrypt any 
requested file using the Vigen√®re Cipher encryption scheme, supporting any 
kind of extension, from a simple plaintext document to binary files.


1.Instructions
**************

Type on your terminal/command line the app name followed by the file to be
encrypted/decrypted and for the third parameter you must input the file name
of the file that will be generated after the encryption process finish properly.

E.g.: $ VigenereCipherFileEncryption myFile output

Note: Don't forget to add an extension to the end filename whether you running
this application on a Microsoft operating system.


